ROBERT (V.O.)
(age 8-1/2)
Dear Moira,
I know that you have a new Daddy in your life and I hope that he is treating you good.
But I will always be your Father and would like to be able to share more of your life with you.
We must find a way.
This silence is hurting me so much.
Love, Daddy

