ROBERT (V.O.)
(age 9)
My dear Moira,
Why have I not heard from you?
Have you been getting my letters?
Have I done something terribly wrong to deserve this lack of contact?
Does Mommy not care that I am still here and that I want to see you?
My life seems upside down without you in it.
Love, Daddy

